      • pages

        public SearchQueryBuilder pages(long pages)
        Sets how many pages of wallpapers to fetch. One page could contain 24 (default), 32 or 64 wallpapers, depending on the preference of the logged in user, set in Wallhaven's settings page.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        the current SearchQueryBuilder
        Throws:
